text: Revere Beach was used as one of the film sets for Black Mass and I have shot a lot of behind the scenes footage in many days. text: FBI Director J. Edgar Hoover had seen evidence that Bulger associate, Vincent Flemmi, was one of the murderers of Teddy Deegan.  However, FBI informant Joe Barboza gave false witness against my big buddy and housemate at the time, Peter Limone.  Mr Limone is now godfather of the Patriarcha family. When I was four years old  I was living with Peter at the time.  When the FBI came to arrest him, I grabbed  one leg of each agent and held on for dear life, yelling: "Don't arrest Peter!  He's my friend!  Run Peter!" The two agents beat me black and blue for several minutes, but I wouldn't let go.  Finally Peter emerged from his attic room and said:  "Kid, why are you always such a jerk?"  and "It's over.  Goodbye" I recount this tale and many other strange ones in my book:   "How I Got Beat-Up by the FbI When I Was Four Years Old"
